It sounds like it's mostly BoB but I do understand that he probably wants to have a certain vibe in the locker room (ala Belickick) and Hopkins didn't fit that vibe. Not a bad guy but someone with enough influence to hurt your design.

I get it. Yet, it shows that BoB is not flexible or able to draw the respect to lay down the law.
Again, imagine Belichick with that talk. I guarantee you that Hopkins nods his head and falls in line. 100%. Why? It's Bill Belichick.

All this says more about BoB than anyone.
